{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/tutorial/a-list-for-designers-portfolio-tools/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"211d6ad3-1ca9-51d0-9967-09f5ac5e8859","excerpt":"…","html":"<p>每个设计师应该都想拥有一个个人网站，既能展示自己的作品集，又能打造个人品牌。可是，做一个网站有一定的技术门槛，比如需要懂服务器、命令行、代码什么的。</p>\n<p>而如今，你完全不用担心这些事情了。现在各种各样的可视化建站工具层出不穷，而且都有着丰富的模板，让我们可以通过拖拽快速搭建一个还不错的个人网站。在这篇文章里，我将推荐几个适合设计师的网站搭建工具。</p>\n<h2>Notion</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.notion.so\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Notion</a> 是一个强大的在线笔记应用，那它为什么会出现在这里？换个角度看，其实我们的个人网站也是笔记，由一篇篇文章组成，而 Notion 又是支持分享成链接的，所以我们也可以把 Notion 作为一个建站工具。</p>\n<p>我用 Notion 做了一个简单的示例。可以看到，我们可以自由排布图片或链接，把它做成一个网站的样子。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8d6ba2cd3484fe7dc68a28a6c33abe7c/0b569/notion-portfolio.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Notion 作品集\"\n        title=\"Notion 作品集\"\n        src=\"/static/8d6ba2cd3484fe7dc68a28a6c33abe7c/6af66/notion-portfolio.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8d6ba2cd3484fe7dc68a28a6c33abe7c/69538/notion-portfolio.png 160w,\n/static/8d6ba2cd3484fe7dc68a28a6c33abe7c/72799/notion-portfolio.png 320w,\n/static/8d6ba2cd3484fe7dc68a28a6c33abe7c/6af66/notion-portfolio.png 640w,\n/static/8d6ba2cd3484fe7dc68a28a6c33abe7c/d9199/notion-portfolio.png 960w,\n/static/8d6ba2cd3484fe7dc68a28a6c33abe7c/21b4d/notion-portfolio.png 1280w,\n/static/8d6ba2cd3484fe7dc68a28a6c33abe7c/0b569/notion-portfolio.png 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Notion 还有一个嵌入的功能，你可以把任何在线的内容嵌入其中。比如说你的设计是使用 Figma 制作的，那么就可以直接嵌入 Figma 视图，这样别人在查看时可以直接在这个视图内放大或缩小，来查看你的设计效果和细节。你还可以嵌入 Figma 可交互原型，这样你的作品集就更加生动了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/737894d438aace9297a3e5d77d06aed3/de062/embed-figma.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"嵌入 Figma 作品\"\n        title=\"嵌入 Figma 作品\"\n        src=\"/static/737894d438aace9297a3e5d77d06aed3/c08c5/embed-figma.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/737894d438aace9297a3e5d77d06aed3/0913d/embed-figma.jpg 160w,\n/static/737894d438aace9297a3e5d77d06aed3/cb69c/embed-figma.jpg 320w,\n/static/737894d438aace9297a3e5d77d06aed3/c08c5/embed-figma.jpg 640w,\n/static/737894d438aace9297a3e5d77d06aed3/6a068/embed-figma.jpg 960w,\n/static/737894d438aace9297a3e5d77d06aed3/eea4a/embed-figma.jpg 1280w,\n/static/737894d438aace9297a3e5d77d06aed3/de062/embed-figma.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>参考：<a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/56662\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">用 Notion 做网站：设计师的武器库v1.0已上线</a></p>\n<h2>Webflow</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0b72b6ca4436b0e4e0f764148bd7cf57/de062/webflow.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Webflow 介绍\"\n        title=\"Webflow 介绍\"\n        src=\"/static/0b72b6ca4436b0e4e0f764148bd7cf57/c08c5/webflow.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0b72b6ca4436b0e4e0f764148bd7cf57/0913d/webflow.jpg 160w,\n/static/0b72b6ca4436b0e4e0f764148bd7cf57/cb69c/webflow.jpg 320w,\n/static/0b72b6ca4436b0e4e0f764148bd7cf57/c08c5/webflow.jpg 640w,\n/static/0b72b6ca4436b0e4e0f764148bd7cf57/6a068/webflow.jpg 960w,\n/static/0b72b6ca4436b0e4e0f764148bd7cf57/eea4a/webflow.jpg 1280w,\n/static/0b72b6ca4436b0e4e0f764148bd7cf57/de062/webflow.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://webflow.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Webflow</a> 是一个可视化的建站工具，它提供了标准的 HTML5 元素，如标题、按钮、视频等，你可以直接将它拖进画布，来设计出符合语义的网站界面。它还支持 Symbol，即将常用模式（比如按钮）保存起来，在各个地方复用。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ea91e86e67ea9209935908e7f01181b1/fc83b/html-elements.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.50000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"HTML 元素\"\n        title=\"HTML 元素\"\n        src=\"/static/ea91e86e67ea9209935908e7f01181b1/c08c5/html-elements.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ea91e86e67ea9209935908e7f01181b1/0913d/html-elements.jpg 160w,\n/static/ea91e86e67ea9209935908e7f01181b1/cb69c/html-elements.jpg 320w,\n/static/ea91e86e67ea9209935908e7f01181b1/c08c5/html-elements.jpg 640w,\n/static/ea91e86e67ea9209935908e7f01181b1/6a068/html-elements.jpg 960w,\n/static/ea91e86e67ea9209935908e7f01181b1/eea4a/html-elements.jpg 1280w,\n/static/ea91e86e67ea9209935908e7f01181b1/fc83b/html-elements.jpg 1556w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Webflow 的设计方式非常接近前端实现，比如你可以设置常见的布局方式：弹性布局、栅格布局等，还可以给元素添加 CSS 属性。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c3c8c4a31c9d9eb54fbd657d40b8d76b/b9962/layout.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"布局\"\n        title=\"布局\"\n        src=\"/static/c3c8c4a31c9d9eb54fbd657d40b8d76b/c08c5/layout.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c3c8c4a31c9d9eb54fbd657d40b8d76b/0913d/layout.jpg 160w,\n/static/c3c8c4a31c9d9eb54fbd657d40b8d76b/cb69c/layout.jpg 320w,\n/static/c3c8c4a31c9d9eb54fbd657d40b8d76b/c08c5/layout.jpg 640w,\n/static/c3c8c4a31c9d9eb54fbd657d40b8d76b/6a068/layout.jpg 960w,\n/static/c3c8c4a31c9d9eb54fbd657d40b8d76b/eea4a/layout.jpg 1280w,\n/static/c3c8c4a31c9d9eb54fbd657d40b8d76b/b9962/layout.jpg 1334w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>除此之外，它还提供了高级动效设置，以及内容管理系统，可以帮助你做出非常定制化的效果。<strong>值得一提的是，Webflow 的<a href=\"https://webflow.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">官网</a>也是使用 Webflow 做出来的。</strong></p>\n<h2>Wix</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://wix.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wix</a> 是国外一款比较流行的网站快速搭建工具。他们提供了丰富的模板，你只需要改改文字图片就可以发布上线了，也就是他们所谓的 ADI（人工设计智能）模式。当然，这只适合定制化不那么强的需求。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/844c4a69e401163e3ea1839d888da5d3/de062/wix-adi.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ADI（人工设计智能）\"\n        title=\"ADI（人工设计智能）\"\n        src=\"/static/844c4a69e401163e3ea1839d888da5d3/c08c5/wix-adi.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/844c4a69e401163e3ea1839d888da5d3/0913d/wix-adi.jpg 160w,\n/static/844c4a69e401163e3ea1839d888da5d3/cb69c/wix-adi.jpg 320w,\n/static/844c4a69e401163e3ea1839d888da5d3/c08c5/wix-adi.jpg 640w,\n/static/844c4a69e401163e3ea1839d888da5d3/6a068/wix-adi.jpg 960w,\n/static/844c4a69e401163e3ea1839d888da5d3/eea4a/wix-adi.jpg 1280w,\n/static/844c4a69e401163e3ea1839d888da5d3/de062/wix-adi.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>如果你的定制化需求比较强，可以试试他们的编辑器模式。在编辑器模式下，你可以更改元素位置，给元素添加动画，甚至还可以添加自定义代码。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/10286ab353f611d32da481a33178b0b5/de062/wix-editor-mode.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"编辑器模式\"\n        title=\"编辑器模式\"\n        src=\"/static/10286ab353f611d32da481a33178b0b5/c08c5/wix-editor-mode.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/10286ab353f611d32da481a33178b0b5/0913d/wix-editor-mode.jpg 160w,\n/static/10286ab353f611d32da481a33178b0b5/cb69c/wix-editor-mode.jpg 320w,\n/static/10286ab353f611d32da481a33178b0b5/c08c5/wix-editor-mode.jpg 640w,\n/static/10286ab353f611d32da481a33178b0b5/6a068/wix-editor-mode.jpg 960w,\n/static/10286ab353f611d32da481a33178b0b5/eea4a/wix-editor-mode.jpg 1280w,\n/static/10286ab353f611d32da481a33178b0b5/de062/wix-editor-mode.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Publii</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://getpublii.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Publii</a> 是一个非常适合设计师搭建个人网站的工具，它提供了很多漂亮的模板，你只需要在客户端中填写内容或编写文章就可以了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f831ba3ad18481a53b88aebe5d192291/ce04e/publii-dashboard.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.87500000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Publii 后台\"\n        title=\"Publii 后台\"\n        src=\"/static/f831ba3ad18481a53b88aebe5d192291/c08c5/publii-dashboard.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f831ba3ad18481a53b88aebe5d192291/0913d/publii-dashboard.jpg 160w,\n/static/f831ba3ad18481a53b88aebe5d192291/cb69c/publii-dashboard.jpg 320w,\n/static/f831ba3ad18481a53b88aebe5d192291/c08c5/publii-dashboard.jpg 640w,\n/static/f831ba3ad18481a53b88aebe5d192291/6a068/publii-dashboard.jpg 960w,\n/static/f831ba3ad18481a53b88aebe5d192291/eea4a/publii-dashboard.jpg 1280w,\n/static/f831ba3ad18481a53b88aebe5d192291/ce04e/publii-dashboard.jpg 2660w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>在 Publii 中编写文章，是用所见即所得的方式。你可以添加丰富的媒体资源，它会为你自动统计字数。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b5c6e0f192be0332348570ab7860d362/dbc87/publii-editor.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Publii 编辑器\"\n        title=\"Publii 编辑器\"\n        src=\"/static/b5c6e0f192be0332348570ab7860d362/c08c5/publii-editor.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b5c6e0f192be0332348570ab7860d362/0913d/publii-editor.jpg 160w,\n/static/b5c6e0f192be0332348570ab7860d362/cb69c/publii-editor.jpg 320w,\n/static/b5c6e0f192be0332348570ab7860d362/c08c5/publii-editor.jpg 640w,\n/static/b5c6e0f192be0332348570ab7860d362/6a068/publii-editor.jpg 960w,\n/static/b5c6e0f192be0332348570ab7860d362/eea4a/publii-editor.jpg 1280w,\n/static/b5c6e0f192be0332348570ab7860d362/dbc87/publii-editor.jpg 1978w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>发布也很简单，你可以连接到自己的云服务器，或者选择 Github Pages 这种静态网站托管服务，就可以一键发布了。</p>\n<h2>RapidWeaver</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.realmacsoftware.com/rapidweaver\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RapidWeaver</a> 采用设计师所熟悉的可视化操作方式来构建网站，它支持设备模拟、主题、插件等。你可以在左侧管理页面，或进行一些基本设置，在右侧修改内容。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ba48635f90592ecdcd0efe4b71fb96c0/e6b01/rapidweaver.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"RapidWeaver 界面\"\n        title=\"RapidWeaver 界面\"\n        src=\"/static/ba48635f90592ecdcd0efe4b71fb96c0/c08c5/rapidweaver.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ba48635f90592ecdcd0efe4b71fb96c0/0913d/rapidweaver.jpg 160w,\n/static/ba48635f90592ecdcd0efe4b71fb96c0/cb69c/rapidweaver.jpg 320w,\n/static/ba48635f90592ecdcd0efe4b71fb96c0/c08c5/rapidweaver.jpg 640w,\n/static/ba48635f90592ecdcd0efe4b71fb96c0/6a068/rapidweaver.jpg 960w,\n/static/ba48635f90592ecdcd0efe4b71fb96c0/eea4a/rapidweaver.jpg 1280w,\n/static/ba48635f90592ecdcd0efe4b71fb96c0/e6b01/rapidweaver.jpg 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>你还可以模拟不同尺寸的设备，来查看在不同尺寸下的显示效果。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/25bb6d78614814a9bed741d43de4ca66/e6b01/rapidweaver-multiple-sizes.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"多尺寸预览\"\n        title=\"多尺寸预览\"\n        src=\"/static/25bb6d78614814a9bed741d43de4ca66/c08c5/rapidweaver-multiple-sizes.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/25bb6d78614814a9bed741d43de4ca66/0913d/rapidweaver-multiple-sizes.jpg 160w,\n/static/25bb6d78614814a9bed741d43de4ca66/cb69c/rapidweaver-multiple-sizes.jpg 320w,\n/static/25bb6d78614814a9bed741d43de4ca66/c08c5/rapidweaver-multiple-sizes.jpg 640w,\n/static/25bb6d78614814a9bed741d43de4ca66/6a068/rapidweaver-multiple-sizes.jpg 960w,\n/static/25bb6d78614814a9bed741d43de4ca66/eea4a/rapidweaver-multiple-sizes.jpg 1280w,\n/static/25bb6d78614814a9bed741d43de4ca66/e6b01/rapidweaver-multiple-sizes.jpg 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>RapidWeaver 还支持插件，你可以通过插件给网站添加诸如社交按钮、购物车等定制元素。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7b9002a3ee6b08828a8f8c53eea80659/de062/rapidweaver-plugins.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"插件支持\"\n        title=\"插件支持\"\n        src=\"/static/7b9002a3ee6b08828a8f8c53eea80659/c08c5/rapidweaver-plugins.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7b9002a3ee6b08828a8f8c53eea80659/0913d/rapidweaver-plugins.jpg 160w,\n/static/7b9002a3ee6b08828a8f8c53eea80659/cb69c/rapidweaver-plugins.jpg 320w,\n/static/7b9002a3ee6b08828a8f8c53eea80659/c08c5/rapidweaver-plugins.jpg 640w,\n/static/7b9002a3ee6b08828a8f8c53eea80659/6a068/rapidweaver-plugins.jpg 960w,\n/static/7b9002a3ee6b08828a8f8c53eea80659/eea4a/rapidweaver-plugins.jpg 1280w,\n/static/7b9002a3ee6b08828a8f8c53eea80659/de062/rapidweaver-plugins.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Gridea</h2>\n<p>目前程序员使用最普遍的一个个人博客搭建方式是 Github Pages，这种方式不用你自己购买服务器，直接将代码传至 Github 就可以生成一个静态网站。但是，Github Pages 需要使用 Git，还是要理解一些技术，对设计师来说有点麻烦。而 <a href=\"https://gridea.dev/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gridea</a> 屏蔽了技术细节，让你只需要设置属性并编写文章，就可以一键发布至 Github 了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/52938273b2c2f9b854c531391364767b/18858/gridea.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Gridea 界面\"\n        title=\"Gridea 界面\"\n        src=\"/static/52938273b2c2f9b854c531391364767b/c08c5/gridea.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/52938273b2c2f9b854c531391364767b/0913d/gridea.jpg 160w,\n/static/52938273b2c2f9b854c531391364767b/cb69c/gridea.jpg 320w,\n/static/52938273b2c2f9b854c531391364767b/c08c5/gridea.jpg 640w,\n/static/52938273b2c2f9b854c531391364767b/6a068/gridea.jpg 960w,\n/static/52938273b2c2f9b854c531391364767b/eea4a/gridea.jpg 1280w,\n/static/52938273b2c2f9b854c531391364767b/18858/gridea.jpg 2544w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Gridea 支持 Markdown 写作、封面图设置、网站信息设置、多语言、多主题、评论系统接入，还支持 RSS 输出。</p>\n<p>参考：<a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/54212\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">《Gridea 让你更方便地管理 Github Pages》</a>。</p>\n<h2>Github Pages</h2>\n<p>当然，如果你真的想了解一些技术，那么大可以去试试 Github Pages。Github Pages 有一个<a href=\"https://pages.github.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">介绍页面</a>，会告诉你怎样通过仓库来搭建一个个人网站。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ff76cfd0f8c3ecc60cc2402ca3728577/0b569/github-pages.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Github Pages\"\n        title=\"Github Pages\"\n        src=\"/static/ff76cfd0f8c3ecc60cc2402ca3728577/6af66/github-pages.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ff76cfd0f8c3ecc60cc2402ca3728577/69538/github-pages.png 160w,\n/static/ff76cfd0f8c3ecc60cc2402ca3728577/72799/github-pages.png 320w,\n/static/ff76cfd0f8c3ecc60cc2402ca3728577/6af66/github-pages.png 640w,\n/static/ff76cfd0f8c3ecc60cc2402ca3728577/d9199/github-pages.png 960w,\n/static/ff76cfd0f8c3ecc60cc2402ca3728577/21b4d/github-pages.png 1280w,\n/static/ff76cfd0f8c3ecc60cc2402ca3728577/0b569/github-pages.png 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>参考：<a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/54608\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">《GitHub Pages 搭建教程》</a></p>\n<p>上面介绍的这些工具，基本是按照从易到难的顺序。其实，如果我们只是想搭建一个个人网站的话，大可不必去折腾服务器、数据库、命令行这些东西，不然很有可能把技能树点歪了。</p>\n<p>对于设计师来说，使用一些可视化的设计工具，去搭建自己的个人网站是很好的选择，因为我们可以把注意力集中在内容上，这也应该是我们的个人网站最核心的东西。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"写给设计师的作品集网站搭建指南","date":"2019/10/22","description":"每个设计师应该都想拥有一个个人网站，可是，做一个网站有一定的技术门槛。现在各种各样的可视化建站工具层出不穷，我将推荐几个适合设计师的网站搭建工具。","color":null,"cover":null,"demo":null,"demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tutorial/a-list-for-designers-portfolio-tools/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/projects/collecting.design/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"想收集设计相关的网址？试试我做的这个网页工具"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tools/figma-icon-automation/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"一种不用离开座位的图标交付方式"}}}}}